<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/394754-is-it-an-easy-and-fast-read----a-visit">Is it an easy and fast read -- A Visit from the Goon Squad? Is it a novel that you have to read a lot because you will be lost if you read some and then come back to it a week or a month later when you have time? Thank you. Renee</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_394754'><a id="like_count_community_question_394754" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/394754?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">7 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F9549746-a-visit-from-the-goon-squad">like</a></span>

